?adret a kkun-id-yaf teṭṭsem imi ur teẓrim ara melmi ara d-yas.
?ebṛet, axaṭer s ṣṣbeṛ-nwen ara tsellkem tiṛwiḥin-nwen.
M'ara twalim deg wemkan iqedsen win iwumi semman lmuṣiba issengaren i ɣef d-ihḍeṛ nnbi Danyel ; ( win ara yeɣṛen taktabt-agi n nnbi Danyel ad ifhem !)
Ah ! A lukan aț-țqeblem kra n timmuhbelt si lǧiha-w !
Amek ihi ara țwakemlent tira iqedsen i d-ixebbṛen belli ilaq a d-yedṛu wayagi meṛṛa ?
Țmesṭerḥabet wway gar-awen s wul iṣfan.
Aql-aɣ nenɛețțab zdaxel uqiḍun agi,
Aɛebbed-agi i yi-țɛebbiden ur yesɛi ara lqima, imi ayen sselmaden mačči s ɣuṛ-i i d-yekka meɛna d lɛaddat n wid yumnen yis.
Yella dinna yiwen wergaz yesɛan lehlak n ubezzug.
Țțamnen yis axaṭer si zik i ten-issewham s ssḥur i gxeddem ;
?er Sidi Ṛebbi, d nukni i d rriḥa taẓiḍant n tideț !
Lmelḥ d ayen yelhan, lameɛna ma tṛuḥ-as lbenna-s amek ara s-ț-id-nerr ?
Ḥadret iman-nwen ur țțarat ara țțaṛ, qellbet ɣef wayen yelhan ama gar-awen ama ɣer imdanen meṛṛa.
?ef ddemma n wusirem-agi.
tafaska n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg useggas n useggas n useggas.
Ma yella nnejmaɛen imasiḥiyen meṛṛa deg yiwen wemkan, bdan țḥemmiden akk Sidi Ṛebbi s tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, ma kecmen-d yemdanen ur nessin ara ayagi neɣ wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, eɛni ur d-qqaṛen ara tedrewcem ?
Atan wamek țțaraɣ i wid i yi-sseḍlamen :
?uma iwumi qqaṛen Akniw, yenna i Buṭrus :
Lɛid i deg ssiwiwḍen deg yiwen umedduz n lluḥ n yitrix n yitrix n yitriberra n yitrix n yitrix-is n yiberriḥ n yitrix-nni.
Mi d-yuder Sidna Ɛisa seg udrar, aṭas n lɣaci i t-id-itebɛen.
Ur ilaq ara aț-țesmermugem ɣef wiyaḍ akken i smermugen kra deg-wen zdat lɣaci.
Tella dinna yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan kessen deg yiwet n tiɣilt.
Ɣuṛ-wat ad yili wayen ara kkun icerken yid-sen.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet.
Win ara yeɣlin ɣef wusalas-agi ad yerreẓ, daɣen win i ɣef ara d-yeɣli usalas-agi ad yețwamḥeq.
Eɛni nezmer a nḥeṛṛem seg weɣḍas deg weɣḍas ?
Imawen-nsen ččuṛen d ddeɛwat n cceṛ ț-țeṛzeg.
Yezmer ad ifhem wid ur nessin ara akk-d wid iḍaɛen, imi ula d nețța s yiman-is ur yeǧhid ara, yezmer ad yeɣleḍ.
Ur bɣiɣ ara aț-țɣilem belli bɣiɣ a kkun-sxelɛeɣ s tebṛatin-iw.
Ɣer wacu i tṛuḥem aț-țfeṛǧem ? ƔƔer yiwen wergaz yelsan llebsa ifazen ?
Si zik wid i gɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi, d wid yesɛan liman deg-s.
Skud mazal tafat n wass, ilaq-aɣ a nexdem lecɣal n win i yi-d iceggɛen ; iteddu-d yiḍ anda yiwen ur yezmir ad ixdem.
Akken qqaṛen : « Ciṭṭuḥ n temtunt ( iɣes n temtunt ) yessalay akk arukti.»
?ẓuɣṛen Sidna Ɛisa armi d yiwen n temdint n Truwas.
Ma d nekk m'ara țwarefdeɣ sennig lqaɛa, a d-awiɣ imdanen meṛṛa ɣuṛ-i.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ?
Iḥuder-iten azal n ṛebɛin iseggasen deg unezṛuf n Akilas.
Atan wamek i t-tɛeqlem : aț-țafem llufan yețțel, yeṭṭes di lmedwed.
Ass-nni dɣa i ɛewwlen ( qesden ) lmuqedmin imeqqranen ad nɣen Sidna Ɛisa.
A d-yas nețța d aqeddac n wat Isṛail n temdint n Ṛuman.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddheb, udmawen-nsen am wid n yemdanen,
Ur t-ḥețțbet ara d aɛdaw.
Nnig n wayagi meṛṛa sɛut leḥmala, ț-țin i gesdukkulen ulawen.
Lɛid n usenduq-agi rsent snat n lmeṣnuɛat imetlen lmalayekkat, ɣumment s tili n wafriwen-nsent amkan-nni i țṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat. Mačči tura i d lweqt i deg ara d-nemmeslay ɣef wayagi meṛṛa.
Lmelḥ d ayen yelhan, lameɛna ma tṛuḥ-as lbenna-s amek ara s-ț-id-nerr ?
Segmi i d-tewweḍ nnuba n leqdic n wedrum n Zakarya di lǧameɛ iqedsen
Ma yella ulac win ara d-yesfehmen, ur s-yenni ara.
D acu ara tinim ihi m'ara teẓrem Mmi-s n bunadem yuɣal ɣer wanda yella di tazwara ?
Taɣect-nni i d-yekkan seg igenni, terna tenna-d :
Acu ara nexdem tura ? Mbla ccekk ad slen belli tusiḍ-ed ;
Skud mazal-iyi ddreɣ, ilaq-iyi a kkun-nhuɣ iwakken ur tɣeflem ara.
Di yal lḥaǧa, ur nebɣi ara a nili d ugur ula i yiwen deg-wen iwakken ur d-tețțekksem ara kra n diri di lxedma-nneɣ,
Anfet-asen ad gmun di sin alamma ț-țamegra.
Ilaq ula d nutni ad țwajeṛben di leqdic-nsen, m'ur ufin ara ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen imiren zemren ad qedcen di tejmaɛt.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Sudum.
d acu-yi, iwakken a d-terzef ɣuṛ-i lmut ?
Ilaq-aɣ ihi a nesṭerḥeb yerna a nɛiwen imdanen yecban wigi,
Yella yiwen n weɣḍas i yi-țṛaǧun... D leɛtab ameqqran yerna ɣeṣbeɣ melmi ara d-yas wass-nni !
Wid-nni i d-ițțuceggɛen ssawḍen imeslayen-nni i lḥukkam n Ṛuman.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ?
Ayen akka i wen-d-nniɣ, nniɣ t-id i mkul yiwen deg-wen : ɛiwzet !
Tella s tadist, yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-tarew, tebda tețɛeggiḍ seg weqṛaḥ n tarrawt.
Ilemẓi-nni, wwin-t yedder ; dɣa yers-ed lfeṛḥ deg ulawen-nsen.
Yewweḍ-ed lweqt anda i țɛeggiden di temdint n Lquds lɛid n weɛzal n Lǧameɛ iqedsen ; imiren d ccetwa.
?-țideț ur a wen-lliɣ ara ț țaɛekkumt, lameɛna kra deg-wen qqaṛen, imi ḥeṛceɣ, ṭṭfeɣ-kkun s tḥila !
Uqbel a d-yas lweqt i deg ara namen s Lmasiḥ, nella seddaw leḥkum n ccariɛa, armi d ass i deg i d-yedheṛ webrid n Lmasiḥ.
Win yesɛan leḥmala n tideț ur ițnadi ara ad ixdem cceṛ, ur yețnadi ara ɣef nnfeɛ-ines, ur izeɛɛef ur yețțaṭṭaf cceḥnat ;
Aql-i nniɣ-awen, ass n lḥisab taddart-agi aț-țețțuɛaqeb akteṛ n wayen yelhan.
Seg wass-nni i deg țɛicin i ɣef tețțekkim di ddnub, tewweḍ-ed lweqt n Mmi-s n bunadem.
ṛuḥet ɣer izenqan, tɛeṛḍem-d ɣer tmeɣṛa wid akk ara tafem deg iberdan.
Awit-ed agenduz-nni yeṭṭuqten tezlum-t a t-nečč, a nexdem tameɣṛa ;
Exdem lmeǧhud-ik iwakken ur tețɛeṭṭileḍ ara a d-taseḍ ɣuṛ-i.
Di yal lḥaǧa, ur nebɣi ara a nili d ugur ula i yiwen deg-wen iwakken ur d-tețțekksem ara kra n diri di lxedma-nneɣ,
Ass-nni ilaq wid ara yilin di temdint n Lquds ad ffɣen, wid ara yilin di lexla ur keččmen ara ɣer temdint, wid ara yilin di tmurt n Yahuda ad rewlen ɣer idurar.
?uma, iwumi qqaṛen Akniw, yellan d yiwen si tnac-nni,
Tella s tadist, yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-tarew, tebda tețɛeggiḍ seg weqṛaḥ n tarrawt.
Yella yiwen yeqqaṛ llan wussan yesɛan azal akteṛ n wiyaḍ, ma ɣer wayeḍ ussan akk ɛedlen ur mxalafen ara.
Yiwen ur izmir ad yeṭṭef amkan n lmuqeddem ameqqran ma yella mačči d Sidi Ṛebbi i t-id-isbedden, am akken i gesbedd nnbi Haṛun.
